spec.expr:
_stream:{fgt.type=${type:doublequote},fgt.subtype=${subtype:doublequote},log.syslog.hostname in (${firewall:doublequote}),fgt.vd in (${vdom:doublequote}),network.direction in (${direction:doublequote})}
| fgt.action:in(${action:doublequote}) AND ${Logsql:raw} AND ${crscore:raw}
AND dns.resolved_ip:*
| unroll dns.resolved_ip
| stats by (dns.resolved_ip,fgt.action) count() results
| sort by (results) desc 
| limit 10

_stream:{fgt.type=${type:doublequote},fgt.subtype=${subtype:doublequote},log.syslog.hostname in (${firewall:doublequote}),fgt.vd in (${vdom:doublequote}),network.direction in (${direction:doublequote})}
| fgt.action:in(${action:doublequote}) AND ${Logsql:raw} AND ${crscore:raw}
| NOT fgt.srccountry:Reserved
| fgt.srccountry:* 
| stats by (fgt.srccountry) count() results 
| sort by (results) desc 
| limit 5

_stream:{fgt.type=${type:doublequote},fgt.subtype=${subtype:doublequote},log.syslog.hostname in (${firewall:doublequote}),fgt.vd in (${vdom:doublequote}),network.direction in (${direction:doublequote})}
| fgt.action:in(${action:doublequote}) AND ${Logsql:raw} AND ${crscore:raw}
| NOT fgt.dstcountry:Reserved
| fgt.dstcountry:* 
| stats by (fgt.dstcountry) count() results 
| sort by (results) desc 
| limit 5

spec.description:
Custom LogsQL filter attached to every query.
Set to "*" to not filter.
See https://docs.victoriametrics.com/victorialogs/logsql/
spec.name: Logsql
